  <brief_title>Dynamic Changes of Circulating Tumor DNA in Late Stage NSCLC Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-centre Observational Study on Dynamic Changes of Circulating Tumor DNA in Late Stage NSCLC Patients Under Gefitinib Treatment</official_title>
