  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A multi-centre observational, non-interventional study is to dynamically monitor the changes
      of circulating tumor DNA (ctDNA) in late stage NSCLC patients under Gefitinib treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
